study_design_info.intervention_model_description:
Cohort 1 will receive 300 mg qd PO, 21/7 Schedule, every 28 days;
Cohort 2 will receive 600 mg qd PO, 21/7 Schedule, every 28 days;
Cohort 3 will receive 1200 mg qd PO (600mg BID), 21/7 Schedule, every 28 days;
Cohort 4 will receive 2400 mg qd PO (1200mg BID), 21/7 Schedule, every 28 days;
Additional cohorts will be enrolled as needed until RP2D is identified
